Rayon Sports vs KCCA FC

Uko umukino uri kugenda

20:24

Rayon Sports irasezerewe

Nk'uko byagenze no mu mwaka ushize ubwo yaviragamo muri iki cyiciro, Rayon Sports isezerewe itarenze muri 1/4 cya CECAFA Kagame Cup nyuma yo gutsindwa na KCCA yo muri Uganda ibitego 2-1.

Muri 1/2, KCCA izahura n'ikipe izakomeza hagati ya Gor Mahia FC na Green Eagles.

Azam FC yakomeje isezereye TP Mazembe izategereza ikomeza hagati ya APR FC na AS Maniema.

Tubashimire mwese twabanye kuri uyu mukino, tuzasubire ejo ku wa Gatatu ku mukino uzahuza APR FC na AS Maniema Union.

15:32

Uko amakipe azahura muri 1/2

Muri iri rushanwa rya CECAFA Kagame Cup:

Ikipe ikomeza hagati ya Rayon Sports na KCCA izahura n'izakomeza hagati ya Gor Mahia FC na Green Eagles zizakina ejo ku wa Gatatu.

Azam FC izahura n'izakomeza hagati ya APR FC na AS Maniema Union yo muri Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Congo.

15:30

Azam FC yasezereye TP Mazembe

Umukino wa mbere wa 1/4 wabaye uyu munsi, wahuje TP Mazembe yo muri Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Congo na Azam FC yo muri Tanzania.

TP Mazembe yatumiwe muri iri rushanwa ku nshuro ya gatatu mu gihe Azam FC ari yo ifite igikombe giheruka yegukanye ubwo iri rushanwa ryari ryabereye muri Tanzania mu mwaka ushize.

Azam FC ni yo yakomeje muri 1/2 nyuma yo gutsinda TP Mazembe ibitego 2-1.

15:27

Ikaze kuri Stade ya Kigali i Nyamirambo

IGIHE ibahaye ikaze kuri Stade ya Kigali i Nyamirambo hagiye kubera umukino wa 1/4 cya CECAFA Kagame Cup hagati ya Rayon Sports yo mu Rwanda na KCCA yo muri Uganda.

Rayon Sports yazamutse ari iya kabiri mu itsinda A mu gihe KCCA yabaye iya mbere mu itsinda B ryakiniraga i Huye.

Umukino nyir'izina uratangira mukanya saa 15:30.
